Package gov.sandia.cognition.text.document

Provides representations for textual documents.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Document
    Defines the interface for a document.
    DocumentReference
    Interface for a reference to a document.
    Field
    Defines the interface for a field in the document.
    FileReference
    Represents a document reference that is to an actual file.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDocument
    An abstract implementation of the Document interface.
    AbstractField
    An abstract implementation of the Field interface.
    DefaultDateField
    A field for storing a date.
    DefaultDocument
    A default implementation of the Document interface.
    DefaultTextField
    A default implementation of the Field interface.
